having a positive effect on you.

1215
01:40:09,530 --> 01:40:12,100
It's my wife. Hello?

1216
01:40:12,100 --> 01:40:14,329
Hi. Where are you? Um...

1217
01:40:14,329 --> 01:40:15,691
Hi. Where are you? Um...

1218
01:40:16,610 --> 01:40:18,369
I am leaving the doctor's office now.

1219
01:40:18,369 --> 01:40:22,009
Hurry up and get home.
We're going to be late for Zooey's party.

1220
01:40:22,009 --> 01:40:22,759
OK.

1221
01:40:25,910 --> 01:40:30,569
I don't want to spend the rest
of my life killing for you, Vivi.

1222
01:40:30,569 --> 01:40:32,579
You're almost there, Ethan.

1223
01:40:34,570 --> 01:40:35,851
Kill the Wolf.

1224
01:40:38,810 --> 01:40:40,609
I am going to need a new suit.

1225
01:40:40,609 --> 01:40:42,096
(SIGHS)

1226
01:40:43,170 --> 01:40:45,054
You heard him.

1227
01:40:51,810 --> 01:40:55,889
There has been a change in plans.
We're leaving tonight.

1228
01:40:55,889 --> 01:40:58,569
Take me to my partner's house.

1229
01:40:58,569 --> 01:41:00,932
He will help me to get out of Paris.

1230
01:41:03,730 --> 01:41:06,729
- Mom, don't ruin my night.
- Why don't you just try them on?

1231
01:41:06,729 --> 01:41:07,879
No....

1232
01:41:09,890 --> 01:41:12,649
TINA: Listen, just at least try them on?
ZOOEY: No.

1233
01:41:12,649 --> 01:41:14,261
(SIGHS)

1234
01:41:21,130 --> 01:41:22,331
Whoa.

1235
01:41:26,690 --> 01:41:29,569
Just smile and have fun.

1236
01:41:29,569 --> 01:41:33,209
Why? I hate these shoes.
I look like Little Miss Sunshine.

1237
01:41:33,209 --> 01:41:35,981
(MUZAK PLAYS SOFTLY)

1238
01:41:39,490 --> 01:41:41,533
- You look great, honey.
- No, I don't.

1239
01:41:48,850 --> 01:41:51,529
(ELEVATOR DINGS)

1240
01:41:51,529 --> 01:41:54,049
- Zoe.
- Hugh.

1241
01:41:54,049 --> 01:41:56,249
- You look great.
- Really, I do? Yeah, of course.

1242
01:41:56,249 --> 01:41:57,497
- You look great.
- Really, I do? Yeah, of course.

1243
01:41:59,970 --> 01:42:02,776
Oh, Mr. Renner, Mrs. Renner,

1244
01:42:03,010 --> 01:42:04,329
these are my parents.

1245
01:42:04,329 --> 01:42:06,489
Nice to see you again.
Thanks for inviting us.

1246
01:42:06,489 --> 01:42:08,169
You're welcome.

1247
01:42:08,169 --> 01:42:10,209
This is Ethan, Zooey's dad.

1248
01:42:10,209 --> 01:42:12,412
Hi. And this is my partner.

1249
01:42:16,690 --> 01:42:18,380
Pleasure to meet you.

1250
01:42:21,050 --> 01:42:22,456
And you.

1251
01:42:23,050 --> 01:42:25,821
If it wasn't for this party,
we might never have met.

1252
01:42:29,250 --> 01:42:30,451
How do you do?

1253
01:42:32,570 --> 01:42:34,454
Enchanté.

1254
01:42:37,530 --> 01:42:38,609
Wow.

1255
01:42:38,609 --> 01:42:40,009
ETHAN: Yeah, wow.

1256
01:42:40,009 --> 01:42:42,611
(CHUCKLES) Kids.

1257
01:42:48,250 --> 01:42:49,417
(ELEVATOR DINGS)

1258
01:42:52,450 --> 01:42:53,856
(LOUD TECHNO MUSIC PLAYS)

1259
01:42:58,850 --> 01:43:00,415
Wow.

1260
01:43:01,270 --> 01:43:03,654
